# install nerd-dictation

[GitHub - ideasman42/nerd-dictation: Simple, hackable offline speech to text - using the VOSK-API.]
(https://github.com/ideasman42/nerd-dictation)

yay -S python-vosk ydotool

usermod -a -G input $USER

systemctl start ydotool.service

git clone https://github.com/ideasman42/nerd-dictation.git


# getting the vosk models

[VOSK Models](https://alphacephei.com/vosk/models)

## english
curl -O https://alphacephei.com/kaldi/models/vosk-model-small-en-us-0.15.zip -C - -o /home/oxo/.local/share/c/livework/202306__stt/model/en/vosk-model-small-en-us-0.15.zip

## swedish
curl -O https://alphacephei.com/kaldi/models/vosk-model-small-sv-rhasspy-0.15 -C - -o /home/oxo/.local/share/c/livework/202306__stt/model/sv/vosk-model-small-sv-rhasspy-0.15.zip

## dutch
curl -O https://alphacephei.com/vosk/models/vosk-model-nl-spraakherkenning-0.6-lgraph.zip -o /home/oxo/.local/share/c/livework/202306__stt/model/vosk-model-nl-spraakherkenning-0.6-lgraph.zip


# running nerd-dictation

## english
130% /home/oxo/.cache/test/nerd-dictation/nerd-dictation begin --simulate-input-tool STDOUT --vosk-model-dir /home/oxo/.local/share/c/livework/202306__stt/model/en/vosk-model-small-en-us-0.15 --verbose 2

## swedish
130% /home/oxo/.cache/test/nerd-dictation/nerd-dictation begin --simulate-input-tool STDOUT --vosk-model-dir /home/oxo/.local/share/c/livework/202306__stt/model/sv/vosk-model-small-sv-rhasspy-0.15 --verbose 2

## dutch
130% /home/oxo/.cache/test/nerd-dictation/nerd-dictation begin --simulate-input-tool STDOUT --vosk-model-dir /home/oxo/.local/share/c/livework/202306__stt/model/nl/vosk-model-nl-spraakherkenning-0.6-lgraph --verbose 2

[Nerd Dictation using vosk! - Invidious](https://y.com.sb/watch?v=msC7KNzqClU)
